| Setting | Value |
|---|---|
| `CERTS_CN` | `{{ cert_common_name }}` |
| `CERTS_DNS_ALTNAMES` | `{{ cert_dns_altnames }}` |
| Network addressing | `{{ network_addressing }}` ({% if network_addressing == 'dns' %}DNS hostname; subdomain routing supported{% else %}bare IP; subdomain only applies to localhost-side access{% endif %}) |
